reviews: Overall nice as it does the job nicely, but if it didn't start to get hot after an hour, i would give it 5 stars.

Likes:
1.Good design
2. Wifi

Dislikes:
1. Poor video quality (even with 1080p). Cant read license plate.
2. Unreliable - instead of recording full 3 mins videos, a number of times it records just 1 second long video. Out of my 20 mins long trip, it recorde
d less than 5 mins in total. It's moody. It will work whenever it feels like.
3. Unclear wifi instructions to setup. You have to read the full manual booklet to figure it out.

Returning mine today.
great quality. looks good. I am happy with it.

review_title: Product Material is not as good. It has a strange bad smell to it
reviews: Product Material is not as good. It has a strange bad smell to it. Fits well tho. Also the product came without a tag, not sure if they always come like this. I threw mine into the laundry as soon as I received it because of the smell. but you cant expect too much for such a cheap price.
